channel.description:
hey all, it’s been over 2 and a half years since i last chatted here. Even though I left the community ive still been making music on auxy as a hobby. recently i released a track for the first time since 2019!! it’s a future bass tune called [Milky Way](https://share.amuse.io/track/kheesh-h-milky-way)
btw can a mod change my name to Kheesh H? thanks
